    <div class="row">
      
      <section class="col-sm-12">
                        <a id="main-content"></a>
                                                                            <div class="breadcrumbs">
            <ul><li><a href="../index.html">Home</a></li><li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work" data-is-top-level="0" title="">Our work</a></li><li><span class="current-breadcrumb">Mental health and addiction</span></li></ul>          </div>
        
        
        <div id="frontpage_mast" class="clearfix"><div id="full-width-guiding_page_masthead" class="clearfix"><div id="leftside"><span id="skip-content" tabindex="-1"></span><h1>Mental health and addiction</h1><div class="leftside-inner">We’re working to transform New Zealand’s mental health and addiction system.</div></div></div></div> <!-- /#frontpage_mast -->
          <div class="region region-content">
    <section id="block-system-main" class="block block-system clearfix">

      
  <div class="bootstrap-threecol-stacked" >
  
      <div class="row"> <!-- @TODO: Add extra classes -->
      <div class='panel-panel left col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6'><div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-guide-text-top standard-block odd" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
        <div class="field field-name-field-guide-text-top field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2>Repealing and replacing the Mental Health Act</h2>
<!--<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" class="fluid-width-video-wrapper" frameborder="0" height="300" id="ls_embed_1631853019" scrolling="no" src="https://livestream.com/accounts/26834806/events/9851605/player?width=1280&amp;height=720&amp;enableInfoAndActivity=true&amp;defaultDrawer=feed&amp;autoPlay=true&amp;mute=false" title="Long-term pathway for mental wellbeing live event"></iframe><script type="text/javascript" data-embed_id="ls_embed_1631853019" src=https://livestream.com/assets/plugins/referrer_tracking.js></script></p>

<p>Join us on Wednesday 22 September at 11:30 am (tune in from 11:15 am) to watch the launch of the Long-term Pathway for mental wellbeing.</p>-->

<p>Can you help us test and refine proposals for new mental health legislation? Public consultation on repealing and replacing the Mental Health Act has closed, and the Ministry of Health is now working on policy proposals for new legislation.</p>

<p>To help us with this, we are calling for expressions of interest from people to become members of an Expert Advisory Group.</p>

<p>We are looking for people who understand the Mental Health Act and how it works. It is our intention that several members of the Expert Advisory Group are Māori, and several will have Lived Experience.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/mental-health-legislation/repealing-and-replacing-mental-health-act">Find out more information and how to apply</a></p>

<p><iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pxIL5Rt_bR4" title="YouTube video player" width="560"></iframe></p>
</div></div></div>  </div>

  
  </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-moh-landing-page-menu-guiding-page-menu-blocks even" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
        
<div class="landing-wrapper">
  <div class="landing-menu-block">
    <div class="menu-links">
              <div class="col col-0">
          <ul class="items">
            <li class='menu-header'>
              <h2 class='h3'><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/he-ara-oranga-response" class="menu-header">He Ara Oranga response</a></h2>
              <div class="menu-header-desc"><p>The Ministry of Health welcomes the Government&rsquo;s formal response to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mentalhealth.inquiry.govt.nz/">He Ara Oranga</a>, the report of the independent Inquiry into Mental Health and Addiction.</p>
</div>
                                                                                                      <ul class='items children left'>
                                                        <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/he-ara-oranga-response/budget-2019-mental-health-wellbeing-and-addiction-initiatives">Budget 2019 initiatives</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                                  <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/he-ara-oranga-response/mental-health-and-wellbeing-commission">Mental Health and Wellbeing Commission</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                </ul>
                                                                <ul class='items children right'>
                                                                            <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/he-ara-oranga-response/mental-wellbeing-long-term-pathway">Mental Wellbeing Long-Term Pathway</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                                  <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/he-ara-oranga-response/submission-government-inquiry-mental-health-and-addiction">Submission to the Government Inquiry into Mental Health and Addiction</a></span></li>
                                                                                                </ul>
                                                            </li>
          </ul>
                  </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
              <div class="col col-1">
          <ul class="items">
            <li class='menu-header'>
              <h2 class='h3'><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing" class="menu-header">Primary and community wellbeing</a></h2>
              <div class="menu-header-desc"><p>The Ministry of Health is working to expand New Zealanders&rsquo; access to and choice of primary mental health and addiction support.</p>
</div>
                                                                                                      <ul class='items children left'>
                                                        <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing/commissioning-framework-mental-health-and-addiction">Commissioning Framework</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                                  <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing/designing-and-investing-kaupapa-maori-community-mental-health-and-addiction-service">Designing and investing in a Kaupapa Māori services</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                                  <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing/expanding-primary-mental-health-and-addiction-support">Expanding mental health support</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                </ul>
                                                                <ul class='items children right'>
                                                                            <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing/integrated-primary-mental-health-and-addiction-service">Integrated Primary Mental Health and Addiction service</a></span></li>
                                                                                                                                                  <li class="child"><span><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/primary-and-community-wellbeing/supporting-people-affected-christchurch-mosque-attacks">Supporting people affected by the Christchurch mosque attacks</a></span></li>
                                                                                                </ul>
                                                            </li>
          </ul>
                  </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
              <div class="col col-2">
          <ul class="items">
            <li class='menu-header'>
              <h2 class='h3'><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/our-work/mental-health-and-addiction/suicide-prevention-new-zealand" class="menu-header">Suicide prevention</a></h2>
              <div class="menu-header-desc"><p>Suicide is a serious concern for New Zealand communities. This section covers the suicide prevention work of the Ministry.</p>
